msgid "Help Us Light Up The Town"
msgstr "帮我们照亮小镇"

msgid ""
"Hey there traveler! We could really use your help. Our people are struggling "
"badly. We can barely survive the night out here. Could you help us out? We "
"are really thirsty. We've lost our water supplies and need to find some "
"fresh water to drink. If you can bring us buckets of water, maybe we can "
"make some deals to get you some supplies in return."
msgstr "你好旅行者！我们真的很需要你的帮助。我们被困住了。我们很难在夜 "
"晚存活。你能帮我们吗？我们很渴。我们的饮用水已经喝完了，需要找到一些可以喝的淡水 "
"要是你可以给我们带几桶水的话，我们可以优惠价给你一些资源。"

msgid "Have you managed to get the buckets of water yet? We are very thirsty!"
msgstr "你找到水了吗？我们快渴死了！"

msgid ""
"Thank you so much for bringing us these buckets of water! We will be able to "
"survive a little longer thanks to your help. Take this. I got this the last "
"time I went fishing and cooked them up for you as a token of our gratitude. "
"Keep helping us out and I might have something special for you soon."
msgstr "太感谢你了，有了你的帮助我们就可以继续存活下去.拿下这个礼物吧， "
"这是我上次钓鱼找到的。你要是愿意继续帮助我们的话，我会送你一个特殊的礼物。 "

msgid "Tell a Countrywoman you have the Buckets of Water."
msgstr "告诉一个农妇你找到水了"

# UnityGame/Assets/Localization/BaseTranslation.cs:46 
# UnityGame/Assets/Localization/BaseTranslation.cs:348 
# UnityGame/Assets/Localization/T.cs:48 
