msgid ""
"Welcome back fellow traveler! You've been a great help to our towns. I was "
"recently doing some exploring myself, and I came across this Music disk, in "
"a chest, that I think you might like. I've heard that these things can be "
"valuable to travelers like yourself. Our King used to tell us stories about "
"these lands up very high in the sky. So high that gravity gets low. He told "
"us just how beautiful the jungles were up there. If this place does exist, "
"could you bring me back some Space Flowers for our towns? It will attract "
"other travels to stop by and trade with us. In return, I'll give you this "
"Music Disk. What do you think, fellow traveler? If this place does exist, "
"can you bring me some Space Flowers?"
msgstr "欢迎！我最近探索的时候在箱子里找到了这个唱片。我听说这种唱片 "
"对旅行者很有价值。我们的国王以前经常会讲关于一个天上的大陆的故事 "
"那个地方高的连重力都会减少。他经常会描述那里的美丽的森林。要是 "
"这种地方真的存在的话，你可以给我带来那里的花朵吗？那些花一定会 "
"吸引其他的旅行者让他们和我们交易。你要是可以带来这些花朵的话， "
"我可以把这个唱片送给你。"

# UnityGame/Assets/Localization/BaseTranslation.cs:46 
# UnityGame/Assets/Localization/BaseTranslation.cs:348 
# UnityGame/Assets/Localization/T.cs:48 
