msgid ""
"Do you have the Space Flowers? We could really use them to attract fellow "
"travelers from all over!"
msgstr "你找到那些太空的花朵了吗？他们一定会引来其他的旅行者"

msgid ""
"Wow! These Space Flowers are incredible! I've never seen anything like them "
"before! Thank you so much for bringing these to us! I can't wait to show "
"them to the others in our village! I hope you enjoy the Music Disk I give "
"you in return!"
msgstr "哇！这些花朵太神奇了！我从未见过这样的花！太感谢你给我带来这些了 "
"我要赶紧给村里其他的人看一看！希望你能喜欢我送你的唱片。"

msgid "Tell a Countrywoman you have the Space Flowers."
msgstr "告诉一个农妇你找到太空的花朵了"

msgid ""
"Welcome back traveler! Our people are doing better thanks to your help. "
"However we still face great dangers from the wild creatures that roam these "
"lands and swim these waters. I've heard of this magical branch called a "
"Sentinel Branch that can help protect us from harm. The branch is made from "
"the feather of a Raven with some sticks. If you can bring us a few of these "
"branches, we can use them to create protective wards around our towns to "
"keep us safe. In return, I'll make sure to reward you with some of our "
"finest Fried LionFish for your efforts."
msgstr "欢迎归来，旅行者！在你的帮助下，我们的人民生活得越来越好了但是，我 "
"们仍然面临着来自这些土地上漫游的和水中游荡的野生生物的巨大危险。我听说有一种 "
"叫做哨兵灵木的神奇树枝，可以帮助我们免受伤害。这种灵木是用乌鸦的羽毛和一些 "
"树枝做成的。如果你能给我们带来一些这样的树枝，我们可以用它们在城镇周围设置防 "
"护结界，以确保我们的安全。作为回报，我会确保用我们最好的炸狮子鱼来回馈你的付出。"

msgid ""
"Have you managed to craft the Sentinel Branches yet? We could really use "
"them to protect out people from the dangers on the outside."
msgstr "你做完了哨兵灵木吗？我们需要用来他保护我们的村庄"

msgid ""
"Thank you so much for bringing us these Sentinel Branches! We will be able "
"to protect our people from harm thanks to your help! Take this. I cooked "
"these and saved them for you. Keep helping us out and I might have something "
"special for you soon."
msgstr "太感谢你为我们带来这些哨兵灵木了。有了你的帮助，我们就可以保护我们的村民们 "
"拿着这个，这是我给你做的。要是你继续帮我们的话我会给你一个特殊的礼物"

msgid "Tell a Countrywoman you have the Sentinel Branches."
msgstr "告诉一个农妇你做完了哨兵灵木。"

msgid ""
"Oh it's you again traveler! It's amazing, these Sentienel Branches are "
"working wonders for us! Our people feel so much safer now! But we still need "
"your help. Our crops are failing and we are running low on food supplies. If "
"you could bring us some Wheat, we can use it to bake some bread to feed our "
"people. In return, I'll make sure to reward you with some Mana Potions for "
"your efforts."
msgstr "哦，旅行者，我们又见面了！太神奇了，这些哨兵灵木对我们来说简直是奇迹！我 "
"们的人民现在感觉安全多了！但我们仍然需要你的帮助。我们的庄稼歉收，食物供应也日益 "
"短缺。如果你能给我们带来一些小麦，我们可以用它来烤些面包来喂饱我们的人民。作为回 "
"报，我会给你一些法力药水。"

msgid "Have you managed to get the wheat yet? Our people are hungry!"
msgstr "你拿到小麦了吗？我们的人民都快饿死了！"

msgid ""
"Thank you so much for bringing us this Wheat! We will be able to bake some "
"bread and feed our people thanks to your help. You can have these Mana "
"Potions. These will help you on your journey. Keep helping us out and I "
"might have something special for you soon."
msgstr "太感谢你帮我们带来小麦了！有了小麦我们就可以做面包，给我们的人民带来粮食了 "
"给，这些法力药水送给你吧。他们会帮助你的旅程。要是你继续帮我们的话我会给你一个特殊 "
"的礼物。"

msgid "Tell a Countrywoman you have the Wheat."
msgstr "告诉一个农妇你拿到小麦了"

msgid ""
"Good to see you again, traveler! The town is flourishing thanks to your "
"help! It's time to add some beauty to our town. Our people have been talking "
"about how nice some flower gardens would be around our homes. Could you help "
"us gather some Rose Bushes to plant around our town? If you can bring us "
"some Rose Bushes, we can exchange another reward for your efforts. Would "
"Health Potions meet your needs?"
msgstr "很高兴再次见到你，旅行者！多亏了你，这座城镇才如此繁荣！是时候为我们的 "
"城镇增添一些优美的风景了。我们的镇上的人一直在说，要是家周围能有些花园该有多好。 "
"你能帮我们收集一些玫瑰灌木，在城镇周围种植吗？如果你能给我们带来一些玫瑰灌木，我 "
"们可以为你换取另一份奖励。生命药水如何？"

msgid ""
"Have you managed to get the rose bushes yet? Our town could really use some "
"beautification!"
msgstr "你拿到了玫瑰灌木了吗？我们的小镇真的需要装饰一下！"

msgid ""
"Thank you for bringing us these Rose Bushes! We will be able to plant them "
"around our town and make it look so much better thanks to you! Here you go! "
"These Health Potions should help you on your adventures. Keep helping us out "
"and I might have something special for you soon."
msgstr "谢谢你为我们带来这些玫瑰灌木！我们会把他们才村里种下的。应为有了你的帮助， "
"我们的小镇变得多么的美丽。给你，这些生命药水因该会帮助你的。要是你继续帮我们的话 "
"我会给你一个特殊的礼物。"

msgid "Tell a Countrywoman you have the Rose Bushes."
msgstr "告诉一个农妇你拿到了玫瑰灌木"

