msgid ""
"It's nice to see you back, fellow traveler! Our town is getting darker at "
"night and it's becoming harder for our people to move around safely. We "
"could really use some help lighting up the town. If you could bring us some "
"Wall Torches, we can use them to light up the towns for our people. In "
"return, I'll make sure to reward you with some of the best cooked food you "
"can find for your efforts!"
msgstr "很高兴见到你回来，旅行者！我们的小镇夜晚越来越黑了，人们的安全出行也变得 "
"越来越困难。我们急需一些帮助来照亮小镇。如果你能给我们带来一些火炬，我们可以 "
"用它们为人们照亮小镇。作为回报，我一定会用你能找到的最美味的食物来奖励你！"

msgid ""
"Have you managed to get the Wall Torches yet? Our town could really use some "
"light at night!"
msgstr "你拿到了火炬了吗？我们的小镇晚上需要一点灯光！"

msgid ""
"Thank you so much for bringing us these Wall Torches! We will be able to "
"light up the town and keep our people safe at night thanks to your help! As "
"promised, here are some of the best cooked fish I could find for you! Keep "
"helping us out and I might have something special for you soon."
msgstr "太感谢你为我们带来这些火炬了！有了你的帮助我们就能晚上让小镇亮起来 "
"并晚上保护我们的村民们！你收下这些烧鱼把，这是我能给你找到的最好的烧鱼！ "
"要是你继续帮我们的话我会给你一个特殊的礼物。"

msgid "Tell a Countrywoman you crafted the Wall Torches."
msgstr "告诉一个农妇你制作了火炬"


